The '''Council of Elders''' was the ruling council of the [[Klatooinian/Legends|Klatooinians]]. They only had control over the internal affairs of [[Klatooine/Legends|Klatooine]], since the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutts]] controlled all activities of the Klatooinians off-world.<ref name="Galaxy Guide 12">''[[Galaxy Guide 12: Aliens — Enemies and Allies]]''</ref>

The Council of Elders was based in a palace built around the [[Fountain of Ancients]], a natural formation in the [[Derelkoos Desert]] considered holy by the Klatooinian people. This site was also the center of the Klatooinian religion, which revered deities called the [[Ancients]] and believed in strength through age.<ref name="Galaxy Guide 12" />

Members of the Council were selected based on age, experience, and their performance in a series of debates designed to test their understanding and interpretations of Klatooinian myth and cultural traditions. Members served for life, or until they were no longer able to fulfill their duties.<ref name="Galaxy Guide 12" />

